        <p>For users that register on our website, we store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.</p>
        
        <p>We collect information necessary to provide our catering management services, including but not limited to:</p>
