        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mt-8 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
        
        <p><strong>Ownership:</strong> Okra Orders retains all right, title, and interest in and to the Service, including all intellectual property rights.</p>
        
