        <p>You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless Okra Orders and its officers, directors, employees, agents, and affiliates from and against any and all claims, liabilities, damages, losses, costs, expenses, or fees (including attorneys' fees) arising out of or relating to your violation of these Terms or your use of the Service.</p>

