        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
        
        <div class="bg-neutral-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-4">
          <p class="mb-2"><strong>OKRA PARTNERS, LLC</strong></p>
